metadata.name: Little Tokyo | 1st Street (1/1)
metadata.description:
// 11/30/2019 
// Original photograph taken in Little Tokyo, Los Angeles, CA (USA).

Little Tokyo | 1st Street is an eight-piece series of fully customized edits to this original photograph. 

This animation will only be available as a 1/1 collector's piece, while the remaining photo variations will potentially be released as an open-edition series. 

The beauty of photography is the ability to tell a story, set a mood, and to share the world your perspective.   

Welcome to my Places & Moments.

Shot on Canon 6D, Sigma 1.4f 35mm

Original Dimensions:
5472 x 3648 @ 24 fps
